classification.purpose: Predict categorical outcomes like region, state, or enrollment type

metrics.precision: Proportion of positive predictions that are correct
metrics.recall: Proportion of actual positives identified correctly
metrics.f1_score: Harmonic mean of precision and recall

regression.purpose: Predict continuous values like population, enrollment count

clustering.purpose: Group similar records together to discover patterns

methods.kmeans: Partition data into k clusters based on distance to centroids
methods.agglomerative: Hierarchical clustering building from individual points

anomaly_detection.purpose: Identify unusual or outlier records in the data
